Name ref="#pmb45258">München</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11402">Ganghofer, Ludwig</tei:ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
